<h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites</h2>

<h3 id="windows-10">Windows 10</h3>

<p>(Tested on Windows 10 Pro)</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/installing/#windows">Hugo Installed and Configured</a></li>
  <li>Git</li>
  <li>GitHub Account</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="linux">Linux</h3>

<p>(Tested on Ubuntu 18.04)</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://snapcraft.io/">Snap</a> (Usually already installed on Ubuntu 16.04+)</li>
  <li><a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/installing/#snap-package">Hugo Installed and Configured</a></li>
  <li>Git</li>
  <li>GitHub Account</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="macos">macOS</h3>

<p>(Tested on macOS Catalina)</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://brew.sh/">Homebrew</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/installing/#install-hugo-with-brew">Hugo Installed and Configured</a></li>
  <li>Git</li>
  <li>GitHub Account</li>
</ul>

